# bookapp/.htaccess

## 1. DENY ACCESS TO SENSITIVE APPLICATION FOLDERS
# These folders contain code, configuration, or templates that should NEVER be publicly visible.

<Directory "config">
    Require all denied
</Directory>

<Directory "vendor">
    Require all denied
</Directory>

<Directory "templates">
    Require all denied
</Directory>

## 2. DENY ACCESS TO SENSITIVE FILE TYPES
# Blocks direct access to common configuration or source files.
<FilesMatch "\.(ini|log|cfg|yml|yaml|env|db\.php|json|twig)$">
    Require all denied
</FilesMatch>

## 3. HIDE DIRECTORY LISTINGS
Options -Indexes